			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing the life cycle inventory (LCI) data for the described process, users should ensure that they are applying this information within the context of photovoltaic module production, specifically for multi-crystalline silicon PV cells from 2011 to 2016 in China. It is important to account for technological changes over the time period and to consider geographical specificity when interpreting results. Careful attention should also be given to the boundaries of the study, ensuring that recycling processes, where applicable, are included, and that use-phase behavior of the PV systems, including energy output and degradation rates, is accurately modeled based on the available literature.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用所描述过程的生命周期清单（LCI）数据时，用户应确保他们在光伏模块生产的背景下应用这些信息，具体而言，是2011年至2016年中国的多晶硅太阳能电池。重要的是要考虑时间段内的技术变化，并在解释结果时考虑地理特定性。还应特别注意研究的边界，确保在适用的情况下包括回收过程，并且基于现有文献，准确模拟PV系统的使用阶段行为，包括能源输出和退化率。</useAdviceForDataSet>
